    "name": "Dubai Real Estate API",
    "description": "Full collection for the Dubai Real Estate Spring Boot backend.\n\nBase URL is stored in the `baseUrl` collection variable (default: http://localhost:8080).\n\nFolders:\n- Sales – upload, list/filter, averages\n- Rents – upload, list/filter, averages",
