    {
      "name": "Sales",
      "description": "Endpoints for sales transactions (sale_transactions table).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload Sales CSV",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/sales/upload",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "sales", "upload"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": [],
                  "description": "Select the transactions-2026-02-19.csv file (or any DLD sales CSV)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Uploads and parses a DLD sales CSV file, persisting all records to the `sale_transactions` table.\n\n**Body:** `multipart/form-data` with key `file`.\n\n**Success response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"recordsImported\": 12345,\n  \"message\": \"Sales transactions imported successfully.\"\n}\n```\n\n**Error responses:**\n- 400 – could not read file\n- 413 – file exceeds 100 MB limit\n- 422 – CSV parsing failed"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK – Import Successful",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/sales/upload",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "sales", "upload"]
                },
                "body": {
                  "mode": "formdata",
                  "formdata": [
                    {
                      "key": "file",
                      "type": "file",
                      "src": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"recordsImported\": 12345,\n  \"message\": \"Sales transactions imported successfully.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Sales – No Filters (Page 0)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/sales?page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "sales"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "page", "value": "0", "description": "0-based page number (default: 0)"},
                {"key": "size", "value": "20", "description": "Page size (default: 20)"},
                {"key": "usage", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "Filter by usage, e.g. Residential, Commercial"},
                {"key": "minPrice", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "Minimum trans_value (inclusive)"},
                {"key": "maxPrice", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "Maximum trans_value (inclusive)"},
                {"key": "areaSearch", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "Free-text search on area_name (case-insensitive)"},
                {"key": "projectSearch", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "Free-text search on project_name (case-insensitive)"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns a paginated list of all sales transactions with no filters applied.\n\nAll filter parameters are optional; disabled params above can be enabled and filled as needed.\n\n**Response** is a Spring `Page` envelope:\n```json\n{\n  \"content\": [ { ... } ],\n  \"totalElements\": 50000,\n  \"totalPages\": 2500,\n  \"number\": 0,\n  \"size\": 20\n}\n```\n\nEach item in `content`:\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"transId\": \"12345\",\n  \"transDate\": \"2024-01-15\",\n  \"transValue\": 2500000.00,\n  \"areaName\": \"DUBAI MARINA\",\n  \"projectName\": \"MARINA HEIGHTS\",\n  \"usage\": \"Residential\",\n  \"registrationType\": \"Sales\",\n  \"propertyType\": \"Unit\",\n  \"rooms\": \"2 B/R\",\n  \"actualArea\": 120.50,\n  \"meterSalePrice\": 20746.89\n}\n```\n(`null` fields are omitted from the JSON response)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
